OL,6,FA van driver who crashed into the back
OL,7,Fof a broken-down car in the fast lane
OL,8,Fof the M4 smart motorway in Berkshire
OL,9,Fhas been convicted of causing the
OL,10,Ffatal collision.
OL,12,FBarry O'Sullivan, 45, was driving a
OL,13,Fgrey Ford work van along the M4 on 7
OL,14,FMarch 2022 when he hit a Nissan Micra
OL,15,Fwhich had stopped in the outside lane.
OL,17,FThe crash, which happened on the M4
OL,18,Fwestbound between junctions 11 and 12
OL,19,Fnear Reading, caused both vehicles to
OL,20,Fpropel forward, with the Nissan
OL,21,Fbursting into flames.
