OL,3,CVan driver guilty of causing death of
OL,4,Cwoman in crash on smart motorway
OL,6,FPulvinder Dhillon, who was a passenger
OL,7,Fin her daughter's Nissan Micra,
OL,8,Fsuffered fatal injuries.
OL,10,FIt was later discovered an unresolved
OL,11,Ftechnical failure on the M4 smart
OL,12,Fmotorway network meant alerts for
OL,13,Fbroken-down vehicles were not properly
OL,14,Fcommunicated in the days leading up to
OL,15,Fthe collision, the trial at Reading
OL,16,FCrown Court was previously told.
