OL,3,CVan driver guilty of causing death of
OL,4,Cwoman in crash on smart motorway
OL,6,FHe did not pick up on "cues" that the
OL,7,Fvehicle was stationary, including the
OL,8,Ffact other motorists were taking steps
OL,9,Fto avoid the broken-down Nissan, the
OL,10,Fprosecution told jurors during the
OL,11,Ftrial.
OL,13,FThe jury found O'Sullivan guilty of
OL,14,Fone count of causing death by careless
OL,15,Fdriving, having deliberated for more
OL,16,Fthan six hours.
