OL,4,Cwoman in crash on smart motorway
OL,6,FOn the day of the crash, alerts from
OL,7,Fstopped vehicle detection radars on
OL,8,Fthe M4 junction 8-9 to 12 had not been
OL,9,Fcommunicated for five days due to a
OL,10,Ftechnical failure on the IT network,
OL,11,Fthe trial heard.
OL,13,FConsequently, the network "wasn't
OL,14,Fshowing messages about any
OL,15,Fobstructions in the road ahead" on the
OL,16,Fmorning of the incident.
