OL,3,CVan driver guilty of causing death of
OL,4,Cwoman in crash on smart motorway
OL,6,FThe technical malfunction had been
OL,7,Fflagged by the system on March 2 2022
OL,8,Fand automatically generated tickets,
OL,9,Fbut they were assigned to the wrong
OL,10,FNational Highways team and with an
OL,11,Fincorrect priority level of "seven-day
OL,12,Fresolution", the trial was told.
OL,14,FThe Nissan had been stationary on the
OL,15,Ffast lane for six minutes before the
OL,16,Fcollision, jurors previously heard.
