OL,3,CVan driver guilty of causing death of
OL,4,Cwoman in crash on smart motorway
OL,6,FO'Sullivan, of Wixams near Bedford,
OL,7,Fwas driving his Ford van at speeds of
OL,8,F74-80mph along that same stretch of
OL,9,Fmotorway for the five seconds before
OL,10,Fthe crash.
OL,12,FA roadside breath test and drug test
OL,13,Fwas later administered and O'Sullivan
OL,14,Fhad a zero reading for alcohol and no
OL,15,Fcocaine or cannabis was detected.
OL,17,FA preliminary sentencing date has been
OL,18,Fset for 24 April.
