OL,6,FA National Highways spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Any death on our roads is one too
OL,8,Fmany and our thoughts are with the
OL,9,Ffamily and friends of Pulvinder
OL,10,FDhillon following this tragic incident.
OL,12,F"While nothing can ever compensate for
OL,13,Ftheir loss, the person responsible has
OL,14,Fbeen found guilty of driving
OL,15,Fcarelessly."
